author: rhuijben
msg: Tweak most of the move-update logic to just create conflict skels and work
items for installing using update_move_list_add(). This cleans up the code
and allows adding atomicness guarantees even when be break up the big
sqlite transaction that is currently around the move logic.
It also makes the code follow the best practices around db operations
(update_move_list_add): Handle tree conflicts and work items.
(create_tree_conflict): ... this and don't install the conflict directly,
tc_editor_delete): Collect conflict and work items and notify
resolve_delete_raise_moved_away): Handle notifications and tc install.
